ieren Un\u00fcbersichtlichkeit und Intransparenz. Die Konflikte um die knappen Impfdosen st\u00e4rken Nationalismus und autorit\u00e4re Phantasien von staatlicher Krisenwirtschaft.\nVon", "language": null, "image": "https://jungle.world/sites/files/_static/jungleworld.jpg", "pagetype": null, "links": ["#main-content", "/", "/", "/", "/thema", "/inland", "/ausland", "/dschungel", "/reportage", "/interview", "/Seite-16", "/disko", "/antifa", "/sport", "/inhalt", "/", "/blogs/von-tunis-nach-teheran", "/blogs/picke-graetsche-aus", "/blogs/jungleblog", "/abo", "/shop", "#searchbar", "#", "https://www.facebook.com/JungleWorld", "/user/login?destination=/autorin/stefan-wirth%3Fpage%3D1", "#searchbar", null, "/artikel/2021/49/durchwursteln-bis-zur-naechsten-variante", "/inland", "/artikel/2021/49/durchwursteln-bis-zur-naechsten-variante", "/autorin/stefan-wirth", "/artikel/2021/49/durchwursteln-bis-zur-naechsten-variante", "/tags/krankenhaus", "/tags/pandemie", "/tags/coronamassnahmen", "/artikel/2021/46/der-naechste-lockdown", "/inland", "/artikel/2021/46/der-naechste-lockdown", "/autorin/stefan-wirth", "/artikel/2021/46/der-naechste-lockdown", "/tags/corona", "/tags/covid-19", "/tags/lockdown", "/artikel/2021/44/der-winter-naht", "/inland", "/artikel/2021/44/der-winter-naht", "/autorin/stefan-wirth", "/artikel/2021/44/der-winter-naht", "/artikel/2021/33/gestoerte-eurythmie", "/inland", "/artikel/2021/33/gestoerte-eurythmie", "/autorin/stefan-wirth", "/artikel/2021/33/gestoerte-eurythmie", "/tags/die-gruenen", "/tags/covid-19", "/tags/impfdebatte", "/artikel/2021/24/masken-fuer-den-muelleimer", "/inland", "/artikel/2021/24/masken-fuer-den-muelleimer", "/autorin/stefan-wirth", "/artikel/2021/24/masken-fuer-den-muelleimer", "/tags/jens-spahn", "/tags/pandemie", "/tags/gesundheitspolitik", "/tags/pandemipolitik", "/artikel/2021/11/der-schock-bleibt-aus", "/ausland", "/artikel/2021/11/der-schock-bleibt-aus", "/autorin/stefan-wirth", "/artikel/2021/11/der-schock-bleibt-aus", "/